      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 38, United States Code, to authorize additional compensation to be paid to certain veterans in receipt of compensation for a service-connected disability rated totally disabling for whom a family member dependent on the veteran for support provides care.</title>
